----------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL SOFTWARE PREREQUISITES
----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Euclid
  Etree database library
  http://www-2.cs.cmu.edu/~euclid/

* proj4
  Cartographic projections library
  http://proj.maptools.org/
  version 4.4.9 is known to work

----------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL OPTIONAL SOFTWARE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

* cppunit
  C++ unit testing library

  This library is used in the unit testing of the code. It is only
  used for testing and not the actual functioning of the velocity
  model software.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL SOFTWARE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

(1) Set architecture, compiler and directory variables in
config/Makefile.config

(2) If necessary, create file with compiler flags.

(3) If necessary, create file with architecture flags.

(4) run 'make' in top level directory

  Note: make will fail in the tests directories if the optional
  software is not installed. You can safely ignore the compilation
  errors. If you want to run the tests and have the optional software
  installed simply run 'make test' in the tests directories.

version
